XBOX LIVE REVENUE INCREASED 17%, DRIVEN BY HIGHER REVENUE PER TRANSACTION AND VOLUME OF TRANSACTIONS. VIDEO GAMES REVENUE GREW 34%, DRIVEN BY THE LAUNCH OF HALO 5 AND SALES OF MINECRAFT. WE ACQUIRED MOJANG AB (MOJANG), THE SWEDISH VIDEO

GAME DEVELOPER OF THE MINECRAFT GAMING FRANCHISE, IN NOVEMBER 2014. XBOX HARDWARE REVENUE DECREASED 16%, MAINLY DUE TO LOWER PRICES OF XBOX ONE CONSOLES SOLD AND A DECLINE IN XBOX 360 CONSOLE VOLUME, OFFSET IN PART BY HIGHER XBOX ONE CONSOLE VOLUME.

GAMING REVENUE INCLUDED AN UNFAVORABLE FOREIGN CURRENCY IMPACT OF APPROXIMATELY 4%.

