PER USER. VIDEO GAMES REVENUE INCREASED $265 MILLION, MAINLY DUE TO SALES OF MINECRAFT FOLLOWING THE ACQUISITION OF MOJANG IN NOVEMBER 2014, AND NEW XBOX TITLES RELEASED IN THE CURRENT YEAR.

