THE MICROSOFT OFFICE SYSTEM AND OUR SERVER PRODUCTS AND TOOLS TO CUSTOMERS THROUGH OUR FOREIGN REGIONAL OPERATIONS CENTERS. IN FISCAL YEARS 2015 AND 2014, OUR U.S. INCOME BEFORE INCOME TAXES WAS

